channel.title: ****~~~MoggyScape~~~**** Development Team Help!
channel.description:
[size=10pt]MoggyScape Development Team 2008![/size]
Hi, I Have been getting bored of my old server ( AdScape ) so i have decided to make a whole new one. Thats where you come in, i have been working on the name for ages, it might be a bit bad, but i like it, my mum was walking down the street with me and saw a cat looking like it was gonna kill a bird or rat. And my mum said "that's a moggy" and i thought it was a good name. and its not taken.
The part where you come in is helping make designs. specs, highscores page etc.
This is the so far subscribed people
(server) *Adamator5 *ownerfraggle *azza p *hello sara * * * * * * * * * * * *
(client) *Adamator5 *ownerfraggle * * * * * * * * * * * * * *
html (webclient Helpers) * * * * * * * * * * * *
If You Want To Join PM me which section you want to be in And i will add you to the list. :P
